headline: MDT Stock May Benefit From New Regulatory Wins for Its MiniMed 780G
summary: Medtronic secures FDA milestones for its MiniMed 780G system, expanding use to type 2 diabetes and enabling sensor integration.

headline: AI firm Ketryx raises $39M, adds former Medtronic CEO as investor
summary: The company, which helps medtech companies with AI compliance, has raised more than $55 million to date.

headline: Medtronic trial of Hugo robot in hernia repair hits primary endpoints
summary: The company reported a 100% surgical success rate, beating the pre-specified 85% performance goal to meet the trial’s primary effectiveness endpoint.
